### EduPortal API - Competitions Controller
### Competition and award management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/competitions
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL COMPETITIONS - Paginated
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET COMPETITION BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET COMPETITIONS BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE COMPETITION - (Admin, Danışman)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "name": "TÜBİTAK Bilim Olimpiyatları",
  "category": "Science",
  "level": "National",
  "date": "2024-05-15",
  "result": "Gold Medal",
  "rank": 1,
  "description": "Fizik dalında birinci"
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE COMPETITION - (Admin, Danışman)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "result": "Gold Medal",
  "rank": 1,
  "description": "Güncellenmiş açıklama"
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE COMPETITION - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

